      "raw_text": "!. r. p. Holt, an extensive farmer in\n1.-THE Okanogan country, was in the\nscity this morning on his way to\nwashington. Mr.. Holt has a scheme\nby which he claims he can save the\ngovernment q considerable amount of\nmoney in the proposed irrigation of\nthe Okanogan country, and he is now\non his way to the seat OF government\nto lay the matter before the survey\ndepartment. Mr. Holt refused to\ngive the details OF his scheme. but\nsaid that many farmers and others\nof the district approved the measure\nand were willing TO invest money in\nthe proposed irrigation project IL the\ngovernment would second them in the\nnew plans."
